<div class="comment-text">
<p>There have been some very good analyses of the managerial class such as this one: <a href="https://americanaffairsjournal.org/2017/05/new-class-war/" rel="nofollow">https://americanaffairsjournal.org/2017/05/new-class-war/</a> and <a href="https://americanaffairsjournal.org/2017/02/james-burnhams-managerial-elite/" rel="nofollow">https://americanaffairsjournal.org/2017/02/james-burnhams-managerial-elite/</a> </p>
