</div><!-- end .comment-details -->
<div class="comment-text">
<p>Ga Gamba: do you know if any good primers on the effects of globalization along the lines you are discussing for those who have a good grasp of economic principles but are interested in learning more about the economic history of the globalization of the last 30-40 years?</p>
</div><!-- end .comment-text -->
